Package: libcognitive-synergy-bridge1
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: opennars-native, libggml1
Description: AGI-OS Cognitive Synergy Bridge - shared library
 The Cognitive Synergy Bridge provides a unified C API for integrating
 multiple cognitive computing systems into a coherent AGI-OS framework.
 It enables seamless interoperability between different reasoning systems,
 neural processing backends, and knowledge representation frameworks.
 .
 This package provides the shared library for the Cognitive Synergy Bridge.

Package: libcognitive-synergy-bridge-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: libcognitive-synergy-bridge1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: opennars-native-dev, libggml-dev
Description: AGI-OS Cognitive Synergy Bridge - development files
 The Cognitive Synergy Bridge provides a unified C API for integrating
 multiple cognitive computing systems into a coherent AGI-OS framework.
 .
 This package contains the header files and static libraries needed to
 build applications using the Cognitive Synergy Bridge API.

